n, but thinking about how we can support other people\u2019s mental health needs.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\u201cI can help others by, keeping an eye out and being ready to listen.\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\u201cI can check in with someone who I haven\u2019t seen or heard from in a while\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\u201cI can always find time to reach out to someone and maybe invite them round for dinner.\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">It\u2019s so important to keep the conversation about mental health <strong>open<\/strong> so that we can keep ourselves and others healthy.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>What things do you for you and for others when it comes to thinking about mental health?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-3969 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.violet.care\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_1472-585x439.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_1472-585x439.jpg 585w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_1472-768x576.jpg 768w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_1472-1200x900.jpg 1200w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/IMG_1472-100x75.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><br \/>\n\u2015\u00a0<span class=\"authorOrTitle\">Brad Meltzer<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp; World Mental Health Day. We are all different, facing different challenges day by day, living different lives. This can be overwhelming sometimes and we can struggle to be with our emotions when things aren\u2019t going the way we imagined or planned\u2026 The staff at Violet Care were asked what they do to look after [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":14,"featured_media":3969,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"s